{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Otherwise, it is ignored.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant interleaved "},{"code":"MLNTextAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CGVector"},{"type":"text","text":" array values"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Conditional expressions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Interpolation and step functions applied to the "},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" variable and\/or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature attributes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNSymbolStyleLayer/textVariableAnchorOffset":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset","abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset","kind":"symbol","title":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNSymbolStyleLayer":{"title":"MLNSymbolStyleLayer","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is a style layer that renders icon and text labels"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"at points or along lines on the map."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNSymbolStyleLayer","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"}}}